ピッキングで解錠する

If you have a lock picking tool and a hairpin, you
might be able to challenge unlocking the door...

Oh no! This is a mimic, isn't it? I wonder what I
should do... Should I dare to open it...?

Oops! I thought it was a nice treasure chest. That
was dangerous. Now, what should I do?
It would be safer to stop, don't you think?
もちろん開けましょう
やめておいたほうが無難ね
※敗北後ミミック化して、エロシーンへ

This isn't an ordinary key, it's sealed with
magic. There might be some kind of mechanism.

Oh, oh, oh! Nice! You came to help me! You're a
good-nice magical girl!

It seems like my friends have become troublesome.
Thank you for being friendly and helping me out.

Well then, as a thank you for helping me, I'll
grant you freedom!
I'm glad it seems like everything is okay.

Thank you, Onoccha! Do you need my help? It seems
like you need it! I'll follow along!
I'm saved! Nice to meet you.
That's nice. Nice to meet you.

Rune Lock \C[2] Theta \C[0] seems to be in place,
it can't be opened with picking.
ルーンストーンを使って解錠する

\c[10]The demon\c[0] is not as powerful as it
seems...

Well... I'll say it... for the sake of our demon
brethren...

I've said it many times, but please don't
underestimate me, Leedis the wise, different from
you.

The secret of the sacred realm... What on earth is
it... If only you would tell me, I would set you
free.
That's enough. Let go of that person.

Huh? Who's there! To think someone would sniff
around here... You useless bandits!
Who are you...? Could it be, a magical girl?!

That's right, I came to rescue you at the request
of Demetri and the others. You must be Leedis.

I knew it, I'm on the right track! But be careful,
that person is one of the Four Heavenly Kings of
the demons! It's the Dark Lord Hadis.

\c[10]Dark Lord Hadis\c[0], are you perhaps trying
to challenge me? There's no need for you to
personally take action... You all, just finish it.

\c[10]Dark Lord Hadis\c[0] Hehehe. I will now
proceed to the next plan. Make sure to thoroughly
torment them!

Ah! They escaped, well, it can't be helped. We
have to defeat these guys.

Thank you, you saved me. You're really strong.
What's your name?

It's me, Konoha. I arrived at the Village of
Divine Trees from Lingarnet and delivered the
sacred white flowers in your place.

Is that so! I'm sorry, did you happen to enter the
room?

I was surprised because if I had seen your diary,
it would have meant death. But Demetri and the
others were relieved too.

The shrine and sanctuary where I am have a portal
that only I can use, and I sometimes use it for
patrols. But the Trial Corridor was unusually
noisy, so I went to check it out.

I discovered that LoliMon was being attacked by
Bandits during the trial, so I thought it was
unacceptable and fought to save them. But I let my
guard down and ended up like this.

Why were you brought here specifically? There must
be a reason, right?

The Demon Four Heavenly Kings, Hardyce, from
earlier is trying to gain control by knowing the
secret of the sanctuary that is targeting the
Village of Divine Trees.

The reason they didn't take me to the Demon's base
and interrogated me here is because Hardyce wants
to keep me all to himself.

Thanks to you, I managed to keep the secret
without leaking it.

But he said something about transitioning to the
next plan. He should be taking action soon.

.........! This is bad... That person, could it
be...

That's right, if the corridor is connected to that
hideout, it means that the path to the sanctuary
is practically open now...

Damn it... Are they planning to occupy it first?
Konoha, I'm heading there first. Please hurry and
meet up with Demetri.
I understand! I'll head there right away too.
I hope Demetri and Marimari-sama are safe...!
ここで単品アイテム入手

The loli character who can use fire skills burned
away the vines!

If there is someone in the party who can use the
level 3 fire skill, they might be able to burn
away the vines that have wrapped around the
treasure chest.
